title: Remodeled Manufactured home
posting_body: ['Remodeled,  14 X 70, three-bedroom mobile home for rent north of Mora, MN.', 'Home located between Mora, Hinckley, and Isle.', ' Located on my Homestead (40 acres) between Knife Lake and the Snake River.', ' Land has chicken pen with coop, small pasture with pond, and play ground.', '$1200 per month.', 'Rent includes, Electric, water connections, sewer, trash removal, central A/C, grass mowing , snow removal,  basic Directv (one box for living room, additional hook up in Master bedroom for $25 more per month), and WiFi when available.', ' Tenant pays;  L.P., account thru Federated COOP.', ' Unit has washer and electric dryer, L.P. stove, electric water heater.', 'Home requires first and last months rent and $1000 deposit ($3400).', '  Twelve month lease, at the end of the twelve month lease the lease may be renewed for a twelve month term if agreed upon by all parties.', 'Home will be available September 1, 2022 or sooner.', 'Please email the following information: How many in the household; adults, children?', ' Ages of children?', ' Any pets?', ' Household monthly income and source?', 'Any criminal record?', ' Small dog(s) if approved by Landlord, NO CATS, prefer non-smokers.', 'Do not call me until 24 hours after you have you have emailed me,', 'NO TEXT PLEASE, I WILL NOT REPLY TO ANY TEXT.', 'IF THIS POSTING IS UP IT IS STIL AVAILABLE.']
